en tracing code; open symbols in-repo via the links.","","| Process (graph label) | Symbols on the path (examples) | Use when… |","| --- | --- | --- |","| **RunReview → App** | [`runReview`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/cmd/review.go#L67-L162) → [`App`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/app/app.go#L42-L62) | Tracing `review` from Cobra into the service container |","| **RunReview → BackgroundShellManager** | [`runReview`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/cmd/review.go#L67-L162) → [`GetBackgroundShellManager`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/shell/background.go#L48-L55) | Tooling / shell lifecycle around review |","| **BuildFromDiff → …** | [`BuildFromDiff`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/context/builder.go#L93-L108) → [`BuildReviewPrompt` / `BuildReviewPromptWithPruning`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/prompt/template.go#L83-L138) | Turning diff + files into the user prompt |","| **NewCoordinator → Prompt** | [`NewCoordinator`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/agent/coordinator.go#L73-L112) | Agent wiring at startup |","| **Init → Dir / CommandLoader** (UI commands) | [`LoadCustomCommands`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/uicmd/uicmd.go#L74-L76), [`LoadCustomCommandsFromConfig`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/uicmd/uicmd.go#L78-L88) | Custom slash commands in the main TUI |","| **Run → NewModel** (review UI) | [`ui.Run`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/ui/model.go#L187-L199), [`NewModel`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/ui/model.go#L101-L176) | Starting the review Bubble Tea program |","","For a single symbol’s callers/callees and process membership, use GitNexus `context` (e.g. `runReview` in `internal/cmd/review.go`).","","---","","## 8. User interaction flows","","### 8.1 High-level journeys","","```mermaid","journey","  title Typical user paths","  section Default CLI","    Run revcli: 5: User","    Config / onboarding if needed: 4: User","    Chat on main page: 5: User","    Commands palette / sessions / models: 4: User","  section Code review","    Run revcli review: 5: User","    Optional intent form (interactive): 3: User","    View streamed review: 5: User","    Follow-up chat / search / yank: 4: User","  section CI / script","    revcli review --no-interactive: 5: User","    Streamed output to stdout: 5: User","```","","### 8.2 Main TUI (`revcli`) — message routing","","The shell is [`appModel`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L59-L89). Incoming `tea.Msg` values are handled in [`Update` L114–425](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L114-L425); keyboard routing is [`handleKeyPressMsg` L465–565](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L465-L565).","","```mermaid","flowchart TD","  M[\"tea.Msg\"] --> U[\"appModel.Update\"]","  U --> D{\"Dialog or\\ncompletions active?\"}","  D -->|Yes| DG[\"dialog / completions.Update\"]","  D -->|No| K{\"KeyPressMsg?\"}","  K -->|Yes| HK[\"handleKeyPressMsg\\n(quit, help, commands, models,\\nsessions, suspend, else page)\"]","  K -->|No| P[\"Delegate to current page\\nor status / MCP / resize\"]","  HK --> PG[\"pages[currentPage].Update\"]","  P --> PG","  DG --> V[\"View: page + status +\\ndialog layers + cursor\"]","```","","**Global keys (main TUI)** — implemented in [`handleKeyPressMsg`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L465-L565) and related command handlers in [`Update`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L114-L425):","","| Intent | Behavior | Code |","| --- | --- | --- |","| Quit | Opens quit dialog or confirms quit | [`handleKeyPressMsg` — Quit](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L467-L475) |","| Help | Toggles full help in status; resize | [`ToggleHelpMsg` / `keyMap.Help`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L272-L275) |","| Commands / models / sessions | Opens respective dialogs | [`handleKeyPressMsg` L500–548](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L500-L548) |","| Tool permissions | `PermissionRequest` opens permission dialog; response grants/denies | [`Update` — permission cases](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L306-L333) |","| Suspend | `Ctrl+Z` style suspend when agent idle | [`handleKeyPressMsg` — Suspend](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/tui/tui.go#L550-L554) |","","### 8.3 Permission and tool approval (main TUI)","","```mermaid","sequenceDiagram","  participant Agent as Agent / tools","  participant Perm as permission.Service","  participant PS as pubsub → tea.Msg","  participant TUI as appModel.Update","  participant D as Permission dialog","  participant U as User","  Agent->>Perm: Request permission","  Perm->>PS: Event PermissionRequest","  PS->>TUI: tea.Msg","  TUI->>D: OpenDialog NewPermissionDialogCmp","  U->>D: Allow / deny / session","  D->>TUI: PermissionResponseMsg","  TUI->>Perm: Grant / GrantPersistent / Deny","```","","### 8.4 Review TUI (`internal/ui`) — state machine","","States are defined in [`internal/ui/model.go` L21–33](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/ui/model.go#L21-L33). [`Init`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/ui/model.go#L179-L185) starts the spinner and [`startReview` L34–53](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/ui/model_review.go#L34-L53) (review kickoff). Transitions are implemented across `update_*.go` files; navigation while reviewing includes [`handleNavigation` / `handleYank`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/ui/update_reviewing.go#L11-L47).","","```mermaid","stateDiagram-v2","  [*] --> StateLoading: NewModel / Init","  StateLoading --> StateReviewing: review completes","  StateLoading --> StateError: failure / cancel","  StateReviewing --> StateChatting: user enters chat","  StateChatting --> StateReviewing: Esc / flow complete","  StateReviewing --> StateSearching: /","  StateSearching --> StateReviewing: Esc","  StateReviewing --> StateHelp: ?","  StateHelp --> StateReviewing: ?","  StateReviewing --> StateFileList: i","  StateFileList --> StateReviewing: Esc","  StateReviewing --> StateQuitting: q","  StateChatting --> StateQuitting: q","```","","**Review UI keybindings** (authoritative list in UI): [`internal/ui/help.go` L38–97](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/ui/help.go#L38-L97) — navigation (`j`/`k`, `g`/`G`), search (`/`, `n`/`N`), clipboard (`y`/`yy`, `Y`), chat (`Enter`, `Alt+Enter`, `Ctrl+X`, `Ctrl+W`), file list (`i`), general (`?`, `q`).","","Streaming from the agent uses commands such as [`streamChunkCmd` / `streamDoneCmd`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/ui/messages.go#L33-L53).","","### 8.5 `revcli review` — CLI branch flow","","```mermaid","flowchart TD","  A[\"runReview\"] --> F{\"--no-interactive?\"}","  F -->|No| I[\"CollectIntent (huh form)\\noptional\"]","  I --> B[\"buildReviewContext\\n(NewBuilder + git diff)\"]","  F -->|Yes| B","  B --> H{\"HasChanges?\"}","  H -->|No| W[\"Warning + exit 0\"]","  H -->|Yes| S[\"Sessions.Create\"]","  S --> P[\"buildReviewPrompt\"]","  P --> M{\"interactive?\"}","  M -->|Yes| TUI[\"ui.Run → Model\\nstartReview + chat\"]","  M -->|No| NI[\"App.RunNonInteractive\\nCoordinator.Run + stdout stream\"]","```","","Core implementation: [`internal/cmd/review.go` L67–162](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/cmd/review.go#L67-L162). Intent collection: [`CollectIntent`](https://github.com/trankhanh040147/revcli/blob/main/internal/ui/intent_form.go) (called 